{"tid":844840,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人諗住打死一世工？","createTime":"2018-10-02T07:26:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-02T10:52:28.000Z","uid":31104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"cdd29c89b5a61bfdd33f73a6d5df6692effd1b95","tid":844840,"uid":31104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T07:26:56.000Z","msg":"出嚟社會做咗大概兩年 <br />\n<br />\n大公司 人工16k -18k 福利好 <br />\n<br />\n上司好人 工作輕鬆 坐寫字樓 <br />\n<br />\n但開始厭倦返工放工，受人管制嘅呢種生活 <br />\n<br />\n好想去創業 但係唔知搵咩搞好<br />\n<br />\n想於工作於娛樂但係又想搵到錢<br />\n<br />\n我嘅興趣係玩具（e.g. hot toys,Bandai 等等等）<br />\n<br />\n有諗過好似開一間孤仔咁嘅野<br />\n<br />\n賣下現貨，幫人訂野 <br />\n<br />\n做飲食嘅話 又需要好大嘅本金 <br />\n<br />\n有冇創緊業嘅ching 入黎比下意見<br />\n<br />\n又或者想創業嘅巴打入黎討論下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"359911b2b9de8519c89aee86b374dc64b8909815","tid":844840,"uid":88887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T07:37:27.000Z","msg":"負債累累<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f161a4e5d90e55aeaaaf9bc8de48f6191ea6ee5","tid":844840,"uid":31104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"359911b2b9de8519c89aee86b374dc64b8909815","tid":844840,"uid":88887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T07:37:27.000Z","msg":"負債累累<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T07:38:43.000Z","msg":"巴打嘗試過？"},{"pid":"939766209e33f75bc41d23d72ca174872b4c3fe5","tid":844840,"uid":161341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T07:53:35.000Z","msg":"當副業玩is ok<br />\n唔好all in <br />\n否則好易收皮"},{"pid":"139dbcf4c04df00445c2f04342dbcbffcd564b66","tid":844840,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T08:01:19.000Z","msg":"而家冇咩人買玩具 買既都係大個左既固定fans<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"424f11545c2bdbeef71a